gomodel:SYNGO_2757  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.2: \"Neurexin Clusters GABA and NMDA Glutamate Receptors\"\nFig.3: \"Neurexin Clusters Neuroligins but Not Dystroglycan\"\nFig.4: \"Purified Neurexin Coclusters Neuroligins with Postsynaptic Proteins\". Experimental description: - \"Hippocampal neuron cultures were prepared from E18 rat embryos...\"\n- Overexpressed Nrxn1; neurexin-1 beta is of mouse species: \"The expression vector for soluble neurexin-1β-Fc containing aa 1-262 of mouse neurexin-1β was received from P. Scheiffele (Columbia University; Scheiffele et al., 2000).\"" ;
